OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Flingering into the evening but soon
OL,7,Ffading. Becoming dry overnight, with
OL,8,Fprolonged clear spells. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly, with some frost mainly in
OL,10,Fprone rural spots. Some isolated mist
OL,11,Fand fog patches. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA bright, chilly start, but
OL,14,Fcloud thickening from the west.
OL,15,FOutbreaks of light rain, mainly for
OL,16,Fwestern areas, during the afternoon.
OL,17,FSome brightness lingering in the east.
OL,18,FTurning breezy. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
