OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,FWednesday, clearing later. Sunny
OL,8,Fspells with showers Thursday and
OL,9,FFriday. Generally mild.
